    // ...
};
```

#### **Constant Naming Pattern Summary**

| Verb | Object | Code | Constant Name | Value |
|------|--------|------|---------------|-------|
| DIVINE | LODES | `ld` | `RBTDGC_DIVINE_LODES` | `"rbw-ld"` |
| AUGUR | LODES | `la` | `RBTDGC_AUGUR_LODES` | `"rbw-la"` (post-gen) |
| ENSCONCE | BOLE | `lE` | `RBTDGC_ENSCONCE_BOLE` | `"rbw-lE"` |
| BANISH | LODE | `lB` | `RBTDGC_BANISH_LODE` | `"rbw-lB"` |
| LIST | IMAGES | `il` | `RBTDGC_LIST_IMAGES` | `"rbw-il"` |
| JETTISON | IMAGE | `iJ` | `RBTDGC_JETTISON_IMAGE` | `"rbw-iJ"` |

